                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110918-34-off190 t18110918-34-cd191"></join>, a mare, value 20 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18110918-34-victim288" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Brill
                  <interp inst="t18110918-34-victim288" type="surname" value="Brill"></interp>
